==English==

===Noun===
'''silver fox'''  (''plural:'' '''[[silver foxes]]''')
# A [[red fox]] with pale yellow or (rarely) silver to black fur.
# A handsome man with grey/gray or greying/graying hair.
#:''Tom Cruise plays a '''silver fox''' in "Collateral".''
# An unusually crafty, subversive or otherwise manipulative individual, often with romantically exemplified regards.
#:'''''Silver Fox''' is often considered a more heroic version of a 'passive-aggressive' or crafty individual with regard to playing off of other people's motives, ambitions and fallacies.''